Subject: drm/i915: Only populate aux_ch if really needed
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 9856308c94ca821fdc6f3440e4d4de069b09677c
